            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日本股市半日跌近2%，日經平均指數上午收市報52812點，跌1034點，跌幅1.92%。</p>\n</div>",
